snippet.title: Road Rage Royale - Official Gameplay Trailer (HD 1440p)
snippet.description:
Discover Road Rage Royale, the cyberpunk post-apocalyptic "demolition derby" for 2 to 4 players. 
Be the last man driving where fighting meets racing.
